Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.09,0:00:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香找出了他幼稚园时候画的画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.08,0:00:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是父亲还活着的时候  一起去的地方的画
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什么地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.94,0:00:12.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:18.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多小岛的话…果然还是濑户内海？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.90,0:00:22.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该不会是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:06.61,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(430,80)\fad(500,500)}因为大家一起走很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.64,0:02:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  你怀疑这两个地方会不会是同一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.56,0:02:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,季节也很相近呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子想不到什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.61,0:02:11.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ぴんっとこねぇっすな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枫  来端一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:13.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.39,0:02:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点心是蜜柑慕斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:19.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  谢谢小香亲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.69,0:02:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也好棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.69,0:02:24.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.69,0:02:26.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是奶奶做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:30.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是试作品  吃完说说感想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:32.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分乐意！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.54,0:02:33.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来  照片上的地方有头绪了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.77,0:02:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相似的地方有很多呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.27,0:02:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:48.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他每逢休息就出去拍照  我也没有逐一问清呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:51.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我记得那次玩得很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.78,0:02:57.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…再来一个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.67,0:03:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.34,0:03:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  你们慢用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.58,0:03:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲待会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.22,0:03:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真的做得很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这个味道好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.66,0:03:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在玉响是不是正在心中飘荡着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.77,0:03:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:29.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  特意要去拍的话则是拍不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早有预谋可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福好像都溜走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.89,0:03:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该用拍这张照片时的心境去拍摄
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话再说回来  这张里面还真拍到了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:49.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得当时这里一定被幸福所包围着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.07,0:03:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.73,0:03:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然小香亲画的这张画里有着什么线索吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  这块大石头
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不觉得眼熟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没印象呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:09.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没用啊…包括我在内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.44,0:04:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家想去那个地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  能去吗  话说到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.92,0:04:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超强力帮手…登场！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.61,0:04:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:28.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:29.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小薰说无论如何都想让我来  我就请了打工的假来这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.90,0:04:37.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才没叫你呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.48,0:04:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我提起今天要集体商量这件事时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.41,0:04:44.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就突然说「啊  好想来」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}真是的  别说了  我不是让你别说的嘛  笨蛋笨蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最近很熟悉濑户内的风景
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.45,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就想了想  小啪那张照片上的地方到底是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…那么…想到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.05,0:05:02.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊  无论如何都想知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  下周日大家一起去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.00,0:05:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.22,0:05:11.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说想去但是去不去呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:12.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超想去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:19.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么下周日早上10点在车站前集合怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.68,0:05:20.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:21.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:23.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一天晚上记得要好好睡觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.39,0:05:25.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.23,0:05:26.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要穿方便走路的鞋子来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.23,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严禁迟到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.38,0:05:31.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}行…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.57,0:05:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  不要忘带换洗的内衣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.07,0:05:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.90,0:05:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…内衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:44.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  今天大家就一起出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.42,0:05:46.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  两个人一起去郊游吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和平常的那些朋友们一起出门
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  下次再和大家一起来坐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.91,0:05:59.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:01.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃猫大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.11,0:06:06.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  桃猫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.82,0:06:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.13,0:06:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐代美姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.11,0:06:21.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.93,0:06:24.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说准备好了马上赶过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲  有困难的话要对纪惠姐说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.93,0:06:31.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都可以依靠姐姐哦  我会用MAXPOWER来守护你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我越说越燃了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.55,0:06:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了好多点心  你要多吃点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.57,0:06:38.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～这是何等的治愈力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.28,0:06:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠我立刻就被萌得坏掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲真是强得不能再强的传说了呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.02,0:06:50.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概要去哪里问了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.50,0:06:52.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是某个小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.79,0:06:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:57.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个香味是…来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  让大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.21,0:07:06.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家快点  错过这班电车的话下一班就要等到1小时10分钟后了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间慢腾腾的了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点  LET'S GO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:11.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.01,0:07:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲快看  是大海
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.48,0:07:19.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.41,0:07:20.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换乘公车  快跟上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.07,0:07:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲  要吃点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我作了些曲奇啥的  现在吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.11,0:07:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:30.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.71,0:07:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  从这里开始再加把油  出发喽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.91,0:07:38.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.27,0:07:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲  背包重吗  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗  要姐姐帮你拿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:47.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许现在正和大家一起走着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经与父亲一起走过的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.76,0:08:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是和大家一起去见父亲似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒…  
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.05,0:08:18.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:20.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:23.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:24.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要拍了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  姐姐  是不是还要往上爬呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.75,0:08:37.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还要爬多久啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概还要爬两小时吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:43.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  两位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:53.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实  如果在这里回去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.76,0:08:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纪惠姐的形象就会在小香亲的心里留下巨大的污点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:59.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好上了  不就是两小时吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.83,0:09:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总会有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:02.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了哦  薰亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.81,0:09:05.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我薰…随便你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.02,0:09:08.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲  累了就和纪惠姐说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系吗  要姐姐背你吗？ 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一点都不累  照顾你两个小时绰绰有余 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:18.06,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}两小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.54,0:09:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  走错了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:23.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合格…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.61,0:09:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到了这里就只剩一小时左右了  再加把油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加把油
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.64,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}一小时后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.82,0:09:36.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}前方恐有塌方危险  请勿进入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就在这吃午饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又走错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:46.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  真是个安静的好地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.32,0:09:47.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坦白说走错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这休息再好不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:52.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从家带来了三明治和汤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈特制的蔬菜烧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.35,0:09:55.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我做的饭团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我准备了沙拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我的甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.82,0:10:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.18,0:10:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.67,0:10:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来吃个三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要吃蔬菜烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.18,0:10:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.87,0:10:11.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错没错  多吃点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.05,0:10:14.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲喜欢蔬菜烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.25,0:10:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  要是我也做蔬菜烧带来就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.60,0:10:21.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做蔬菜烧味的曲奇怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:23.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  好新奇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.51,0:10:27.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个酱汁好好吃  麻音亲特制的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  西红柿好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.75,0:10:35.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个  佐代美姐姐  还有大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.67,0:10:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是谢谢你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:42.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者该说  为了我们这事还真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.68,0:10:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陪我们来做这么累人的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.45,0:10:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.11,0:10:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  虽然确实很累人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  但是很开心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.72,0:11:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:04.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小啪的爸爸的那张旧照片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.38,0:11:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不知不觉间已经成为大家的回忆了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:15.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:20.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然记不起是在何时何地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:31.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我确实感受到了曾经那似乎装满了整颗心的  就像是要溢出来了一样的喜悦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:38.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那张照片唤回了大家就快要忘却了的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.10,0:11:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  各自的回忆虽然都不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:46.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是会不由地觉得那珍贵而又令人怀念的风景就在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.45,0:11:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家想去看看那照片上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的…回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.70,0:11:58.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  吃饱了就出发了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.42,0:12:00.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.02,0:12:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了  就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.06,0:12:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:23.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦  小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.68,0:12:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方居然有这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有像那张照片上能远望的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:37.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.36,0:12:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等我  小香亲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.67,0:12:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与那张照片稍微有点不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.55,0:12:52.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  好像是不太一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.07,0:12:54.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.15,0:12:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  来这里真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.53,0:13:01.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赞成小啪亲  辛苦没有白费呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.06,0:13:03.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这风的味道  还是第一次闻到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.07,0:13:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风的声音也和小镇上听到的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.57,0:13:15.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好怀念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.72,0:13:20.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪也许真的和爸爸来过这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:23.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…也许
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.57,0:13:33.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然与照片上的地方不同  但是有种和爸爸相见了的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  那里成为了我们新的回忆之地
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.78,0:13:45.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  大家都有带内衣来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带是带了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.04,0:13:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等公车的这段时间去个好地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.62,0:13:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶诶  澡堂  还是和小香亲一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.16,0:13:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他平常都是和我一起洗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈  感情真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.19,0:14:02.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了不行了不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.91,0:14:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面  我是沢渡枫  这是我弟弟沢渡香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫薰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:37.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塙佐代美  是小薰的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:40.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我做完事前  大家一起先在院子里玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.04,0:14:44.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:46.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有爸爸和小香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.35,0:14:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为有工作  在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:04.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒  啪嗒…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.03,0:15:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.99,0:15:13.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫今天开始就叫小啪了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.71,0:15:15.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:19.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.96,0:15:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.07,0:15:24.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和爸爸要玩什么呢  小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:26.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.16,0:15:38.57,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(450,200)\fad(500,500)}因为是那一日的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:43.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  小啪亲是姐姐给命名的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.23,0:15:44.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来还真是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.11,0:15:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那种事…大家来看这个啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:49.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.67,0:15:55.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.58,0:15:57.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:02.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说这个超有趣瞬间系列到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.51,0:16:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请叫我抓拍猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.10,0:16:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓拍猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错过任何一个决定性的瞬间的抓拍猎人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那秘诀究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.99,0:16:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…那人的情况是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下快门的时候  最佳镜头总是不期而至
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.64,0:16:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说没有秘诀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:29.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.95,0:16:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果爱好是拍照的话  也许能让别人教你各种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:42.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点上啊  貌似她还没有到爱好的程度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:46.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在她专注于…小型秘境研究
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小型秘境？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  就在很近的地方  但却可以有种外出玩玩的感觉的秘境地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多就是这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.02,0:16:59.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  虽然说得很可爱但是我不会上当的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.54,0:17:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终究还是秘境吧  要爬两小时或者四小时的山路的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…而且她现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在寻找第二候选地研究中哦  纪惠君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.58,0:17:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}啊啊啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.86,0:17:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你们安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:17.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是…十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.24,0:17:24.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蛋糕真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.57,0:17:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  好幸福呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:27.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…  您是沢渡枫小姐的母亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.30,0:17:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.83,0:17:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是志保美理穗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.96,0:17:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给  洗好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.81,0:17:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然Maestro也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那照片上的地方是哪里我也没问过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:59.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.24,0:18:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.09,0:18:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是要等姐姐的调查结果出来后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:08.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家再一起去吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香亲会不会在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可能还没有来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:20.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…要不要去小学接他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.32,0:18:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张也是小枫拍的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:32.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候她比她爸爸都熟悉相机的用法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  焦距一下就调好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.78,0:18:38.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下午好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.83,0:18:39.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.46,0:18:40.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.38,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎你们回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！  志保美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.39,0:18:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:49.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找你玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.18,0:18:54.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正在看沢渡小姐和你爸爸拍的照片呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.27,0:18:56.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.06,0:19:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爸爸拍的照片  无论哪张都让人感觉暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.36,0:19:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像把当时你爸爸的那种心情直接拍下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沢渡小姐的照片  则感觉让人愉悦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.44,0:19:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像笑容要从照片中溢出般
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.81,0:19:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是很有沢渡小姐的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的感觉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.50,0:19:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不由得有这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.39,0:19:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如看看刚才洗好的照片吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.52,0:19:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  我都还没看呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  让我看让我看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:32.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.84,0:19:36.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些是周日和大家一起出去时拍的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:38.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.12,0:19:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她笑了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.43,0:19:46.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被嘲笑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.68,0:19:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有拍到玉响呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.91,0:19:55.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦哦  这张小香亲好帅气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:02.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沢渡小姐总是非常努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实很努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是都拍得不好…果然技术很差
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.29,0:20:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别在意  别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.57,0:20:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.07,0:20:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.84,0:20:18.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奶奶…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明不用这样安慰我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.10,0:20:26.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是安慰  因为我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.40,0:20:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些照片里都确实地映出了努力拍摄的小枫的身姿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如奶奶说的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每张照片里都有小枫的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.13,0:20:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你爸爸的照片里 也有你爸爸的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心与心相互交融了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  沢渡小姐  稍微一起去散下步吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  我们出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:58.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看小枫紧张成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.34,0:21:02.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:04.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:08.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…奶奶  下次做糕点能让我帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.97,0:21:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  那太好了  请一定来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.56,0:21:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  太好了  试作品的蜜柑慕斯很好吃  是要做那个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正好要去做这个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.76,0:21:20.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:26.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沢渡小姐  要一直将摄影喜欢下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.02,0:21:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  好的  那一定没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.60,0:21:38.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为偶尔也有那种为了拍好而努力过头  最终讨厌拍照的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上…那就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.36,0:21:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,技术一直原地踏步  变得厌倦甚至很长时间没有拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.78,0:21:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是某一次呆呆地看着天空  突然好想拍拍看那片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:21:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就拍了天空的照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.12,0:21:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:22:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时没有多想  呆呆地拍下的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.21,0:22:06.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得是最有自己的感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.69,0:22:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后就再一次喜欢上拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:10.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.83,0:22:15.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不想  呆呆地去拍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔这样也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很擅长发呆的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能帮我们拍张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  抬着那里  然后喊1…2…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.11,0:22:31.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.92,0:22:33.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  1…2…  
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.56,0:22:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:40.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}好  要拍喽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:41.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  照片并不是要拍给谁看的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.42,0:22:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是该试试为了自己而去拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.29,0:22:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.86,0:22:48.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要硬来  想拍就拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.13,0:22:55.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于决定第二候选地了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.76,0:22:56.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.70,0:22:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会是哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.18,0:23:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照惯例这不会公布
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:07.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这次是能坐车坐到半路  秘境等级为C的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.20,0:23:09.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那是几级啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:14.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全体参加  实行日是…下个星期天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:16.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,血色星期天吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,PopSub,0000,0000,0000,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改 
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}于是  星期天…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.38,0:23:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  快坐上来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.89,0:23:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不坐上来的话就要走着去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.06,0:23:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真是究极的选择…由做好觉悟的人开始上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不晕车吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.83,0:23:43.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是车子本身是没问题…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.11,0:24:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  多么美妙的风景啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.46,0:24:10.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到达
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.20,0:24:15.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了这里的话  接下来只需走…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  1…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.68,0:24:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.00,0:24:19.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分钟？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.41,0:24:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1小时？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.69,0:24:23.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,增加了！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.83,0:24:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就快到了  大家加油
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:36.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  原来是指20分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.90,0:24:40.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2小时怎么说都太扯了点呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.45,0:24:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.57,0:25:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗  小香
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:05.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.34,0:25:07.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.39,0:25:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.51,0:25:12.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小香等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.47,0:25:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以四处乱跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.33,0:25:17.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小啪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.03,0:25:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.69,0:25:22.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.56,0:25:28.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  好像…扭到脚了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.42,0:25:29.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.54,0:25:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  还能走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.93,0:25:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大概
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.30,0:25:38.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是叫人来比较好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.64,0:25:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢  最好不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.35,0:25:41.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.46,0:25:44.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个电话给附近的人试试
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.12,0:25:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是我的绝对推荐地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.82,0:25:52.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特地让您带我们来真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.60,0:25:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜一碟
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.23,0:25:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.11,0:25:59.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  到了  绝妙的景致之地
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.40,0:26:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.67,0:26:01.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.38,0:26:04.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是拍那张照片的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.84,0:26:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.04,0:26:10.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  Maestro
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.11,0:26:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.55,0:26:15.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说  那张照片是在这里拍下的？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.84,0:26:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.77,0:26:20.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么漂亮的地方…一定是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.05,0:26:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  暂时就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.72,0:26:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫  我来背你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.37,0:26:28.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？  那样太不好意思了…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.89,0:26:30.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.58,0:26:33.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.02,0:26:35.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.99,0:26:37.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不重
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.18,0:26:43.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小枫姐被背背  小枫姐被背背  小枫姐变孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.50,0:26:45.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小香真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.02,0:26:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不去背小香亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.81,0:26:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有心无力…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.92,0:26:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮的大海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.93,0:26:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.58,0:26:57.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起拍张照怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.78,0:26:59.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.28,0:27:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.77,0:27:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  这片海总觉得好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.45,0:27:14.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.52,0:27:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这里  小香画里面的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.12,0:27:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.04,0:27:24.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.12,0:27:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝日山？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.21,0:27:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.12,0:27:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,画里的那片黑色…那个不是石头
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.26,0:27:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个一定是爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.39,0:27:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小香是在爸爸的背上看到了那片风景的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.55,0:27:49.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…爸爸的背上…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.40,0:28:36.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～是的  是的是的是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.40,0:28:39.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了小枫姐  见到爸爸了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.25,0:28:45.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…见到了呢  和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.12,0:28:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道这里是不是那照片上的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.98,0:28:56.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是能够和大家一起来到这里  
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.89,0:29:01.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是多亏了爸爸留给我的相机和照片
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.83,0:29:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能直接见面
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.95,0:29:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在照片中确实映出了…爸爸的心
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.83,0:29:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是从此以后也会一成不变的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.54,0:29:23.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照片果然很不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.91,0:29:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.10,0:31:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择这里的停车场的话  只要20秒钟就能到山顶
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.89,0:31:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了  哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.70,0:31:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
